---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "June 18, 2026";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Solstice Cipher" description="Privacy policy for Solstice Cipher — a free browser-based puzzle game built in Godot 4.">
	<section style="padding-top: 4rem;">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="privacy-content">
				<a href="/projects/solstice-cipher" class="back-link">← Back to Solstice Cipher</a>
				<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
				<p class="app-name">for <strong>Solstice Cipher</strong></p>
				<p class="last-updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

				<div class="highlight-box">
					<p>Solstice Cipher is a free, browser-based puzzle game. There is no account, no login, and no tracking. The game runs entirely in your browser, and your progress stays on your device.</p>
				</div>

				<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
				<p>
					Solstice Cipher does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. The game does not ask you to create an account or sign in, and no personally identifiable information is requested at any point.
				</p>

				<h2>2. Game Progress and Local Storage</h2>
				<p>
					Your puzzle progress and preferences are saved locally in your browser using <code>localStorage</code>. This data remains on your device and is never sent to us or any third party. Clearing your browser data or site storage will remove this information.
				</p>

				<h2>3. Hosting</h2>
				<p>
					The game is hosted on static hosting providers (GitHub Pages and Vercel). These providers may record standard server logs — such as IP address, request time, and browser type — for the purpose of serving and securing the site. We do not use this data to identify or track you. See their respective policies:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Privacy Statement</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vercel Privacy Policy</a></li>
				</ul>

				<h2>4. Advertising and In-App Purchases</h2>
				<p>
					Solstice Cipher contains no advertisements and offers no in-app purchases. The game is free to play in its entirety.
				</p>

				<h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
				<p>
					Aside from the static hosting providers mentioned above, Solstice Cipher does not integrate any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.
				</p>

				<h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
				<p>
					Solstice Cipher is suitable for general audiences and does not knowingly collect any personal information from children or any other users. No data is gathered from players of any age.
				</p>

				<h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
				<p>
					Because all game data is stored locally in your browser, you remain in full control of it at all times. You can:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Clear your progress at any time by clearing your browser's site data for this game</li>
					<li>Play in a private/incognito window to avoid storing any data on your device</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
				<p>
					We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Continued use of the game after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
				</p>

				<h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
				<p>
					If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@benihkode.web.id">hello@benihkode.web.id</a>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.privacy-content {
		max-width: 680px;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}
	h1 { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
	.app-name { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
	.last-updated {
		font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	h2 { margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 1.3rem; }
	p { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
	ul {
		list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
	a { color: var(--accent); }
	code {
		font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.9em;
		background: var(--bg-card); padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem;
		border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
	}
	.highlight-box {
		background: var(--surface-2, rgba(255,255,255,0.05));
		border: 1px solid var(--border, rgba(255,255,255,0.1));
		border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	.highlight-box p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--text-primary);
	}
</style>
